\[
\vec{E}(z,t) = E_0 \left[ \hat{x} \sin(kz - \omega t) + \hat{y} \cos(kz - \omega t) \right]
\]
where \(\hat{x}\) and \(\hat{y}\) are unit vectors in the \(x\)- and \(y\)-directions, respectively.

